data.description:
Check out this Cozy 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home in the heart of Silverado Ranch. This home comes with
all Stainless steel appliances, a new washer and dryer as well as brand-new HVAC System. Home Features
1 car garage, wonderful front porch great for a BBQ, kitchen overlooks the family room. This property is
conveniently located close to the 15 freeway with access to the LV Strip! The community includes a
wonderful Pool. Move-in ready home (new paint, new carpets and new baseboards)
